articles.description: Dylan Osetkowski scored 21 points, Texas slowed national scoring leader Trae Young, and the Longhorns beat No. 23 Oklahoma 77-66 on Saturday to extend the Sooners' losing streak to five games.
articles.headline: Osetkowski scores 21 as Texas tops No. 23 Oklahoma 77-66

articles.description: Miami's Lonnie Walker IV drives down the baseline and throws down an emphatic two-handed dunk.
articles.headline: Walker elevates for two-handed finish

images.caption: Miami's Lonnie Walker IV drives down the baseline and throws down an emphatic two-handed dunk.
images.name: Walker elevates for two-handed finish

articles.description: A.J. Davis scored 19 points, with a career-best four 3-pointers, and grabbed 10 rebounds for his seventh double-double of the season and Central Florida cruised past short-handed SMU 52-37 on Saturday.
articles.headline: Davis has double-double; UCF tops short-handed SMU 52-37

articles.description: After grabbing the offensive rebound, Syracuse's Marek Dolezaj whips a behind-the-back pass to Oshae Brissett to set up a contested layup.
articles.headline: Dolezaj's behind-the-back dime sets up layup

images.caption: After grabbing the offensive rebound, Syracuse's Marek Dolezaj whips a behind-the-back pass to Oshae Brissett to set up a contested layup.
images.name: Dolezaj's behind-the-back dime sets up layup

articles.description: Steve Nash, fellow star point guard Jason Kidd, Grant Hill and Ray Allen are among the 13 finalists for induction into the Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame.
articles.headline: Steve Nash, Jason Kidd among 13 finalists for Basketball Hall of Fame

images.caption: Steve Nash, left, ranks third in NBA assists, behind only Jason Kidd, right, and career leader John Stockton. Nash and Kidd are among the 13 finalists for induction into the Naismith Memorial Basketball Hall of Fame in 2018.
images.name: Jason Kidd and Steve Nash [600x400] - Copy

images.caption: Two-time NBA champ Ray Allen is announced as a finalist for the Basketball Hall of Fame.
images.name: Allen named as 2018 Hall of Fame finalist
